flowchart TD
  Start([Start Session]) --> Auth{Valid JWT Session?}

  Auth -- No --> LoginChoice{Login Method}
  LoginChoice -- Email --> EmailLogin[Submit email/password]
  LoginChoice -- Google --> OAuthStart[Start Google OAuth]
  OAuthStart --> OAuthExchange[Exchange one-time code]
  EmailLogin --> LoginOk{Auth Success?}
  OAuthExchange --> LoginOk
  LoginOk -- No --> AuthError[Show auth error + retry]
  AuthError --> LoginChoice
  LoginOk -- Yes --> Bootstrap[Load profile + preference]

  Auth -- Yes --> Bootstrap
  Bootstrap --> ProfileGate{Onboarding complete?}
  ProfileGate -- No --> Onboarding[Complete profile and preferences]
  Onboarding --> OnboardingSaved{Save successful?}
  OnboardingSaved -- No --> OnboardingRetry[Show validation errors]
  OnboardingRetry --> Onboarding
  OnboardingSaved -- Yes --> Feed

  ProfileGate -- Yes --> Feed[Load discovery feed]
  Feed --> FeedOk{Feed load success?}
  FeedOk -- No --> FeedRetry[Show retry button]
  FeedRetry --> Feed
  FeedOk -- Yes --> SwipeChoice{Swipe decision}

  SwipeChoice -- Like --> SaveLike[POST /discovery/swipe LIKE]
  SwipeChoice -- Pass --> SavePass[POST /discovery/swipe PASS]
  SavePass --> Feed

  SaveLike --> SwipeStored{Swipe stored?}
  SwipeStored -- No --> SwipeError[Display transient failure]
  SwipeError --> Feed
  SwipeStored -- Yes --> Mutual{Mutual like?}
  Mutual -- No --> Feed
  Mutual -- Yes --> MatchCreate[Create Match + Conversation]

  MatchCreate --> MatchesPage[Open matches page]
  MatchesPage --> ChatOpen[Enter chat room]
  ChatOpen --> SendMsg[Send message via Socket.IO]
  SendMsg --> End([End or continue chatting])
